Revision history for Dist-Zilla-Lump

0.07    2015-05-15 (PERLANCAR) (unreleased)

        - Rename dist from DZP-PERLANCAR-AddDeps to DZP-Lump.

        [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGES]

        - Change configuration from 'module' to 'lump_dist' and
          'lump_dist_and_deps'.

        - Munge files, replace #LUMP_MODULES and #LUMP_DISTS with 'our
          @LUMP_MODULES = ...' and 'our @LUMPED_DIST = ...' to help other tools
          (e.g. lint-prereqs) know the lumped contents.


0.06    2015-05-15 (PERLANCAR)

	- [Bugfix] Forgot (again) to add the added modules themselves,
	  derp.


0.05    2015-05-15 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [Bugfix] Typo.


0.04    2015-05-15 (PERLANCAR)

        [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGES]

        - To avoid the added modules being in the prereqs themselves, now the
          modules to be added are specified in the 'modules' plugin
          configuration instead of in the Prereqs section.


0.03    2015-05-15 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [Bugfix] Avoid proliferation of ' version xxx' text.


0.02    2015-05-15 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Complete incomplete documentation.


0.01     2015-05-15 (PERLANCAR)

         - First release.
